snippet.title: Half-Life: Sum - Trailer
snippet.description:
Trailer for my mod Half-Life: Sum for the original Half-Life. 

Download here: https://www.moddb.com/mods/half-life-sum/downloads/half-life-sum

Song is called "The Burden of Seven Billion" by Cattle Decapitation.
